  "notes": "Live Admin GraphQL 2026-04 public evidence shows fulfillmentServiceCreate applies the GraphQL default requiresShippingMethod: true when the argument is omitted. The same default is re-applied on fulfillmentServiceUpdate, so updating a record that was previously created with requiresShippingMethod: false and omitting the argument resets the stored value to true. Strict payload/read targets compare the selected fulfillment-service resource, with only live-vs-synthetic IDs carved out."
